summary: Experienced Accounting and Legal Assistant with a demonstrated history of working in the financial services industry. Proven talent for aligning institutional strategy and objectives with established public relations management models to achieve maximum operational input.Growth-focused team player with expertise in professional writing, media liaisons, administrative management, travel and career counseling, translation, event planning and coordination, and project management. Exceptional administrator with keen interpersonal, communication, and organizational skills, as well as scheduling, official correspondence, and website maintenance expertise.
